11:44 AM Defendant Princeton Lee Witherspoon in court, in custody.  Attorney Joseph Foster Rosenthal in court for Princeton Lee Witherspoon.  Attorney Angela M Wilson in court for State of Wisconsin. Attorney Rosenthal states defendant lifelong resident of the area with local ties. Notes not violent offense charges. Court questions if defendant was on supervision when offense occurred. Attorney Rosenthal notes defendant was on supervision when this offense occurred. Defendant makes statement to the Court. Court denies bail modification.
